TO convert the python file into executable:

1> Install module named "pyinstaller":
	"pip install pyinstaller"

2> Go to particular file location where the python file is saved.

3> Open terminal at the particular directory:
	"pyinstaller --onefile Python_script.py"

4> If we don't want the console to be running in background:
	"pyinstaller --noconsole Python_scipt.py"
